text: Coonambula is a locality in the North Burnett Region, Queensland, Australia. In the , Coonambula had a population of 70 people. == Geography == The locality is bounded to the east by the Burnett River. == Education == There are no schools in the locality. The nearest primary schools are in Mundubbera and Eidsvold. == References == Category:North Burnett Region Category:Localities in Queensland
title: Coonambula, Queensland
